rm / l2norm(t)\n\nThe gradient seems t / t * clip_norm, right ? I think the result is undefined when t == 0.\n@alextp Could you please comment or reassign?", "body": "According to its [API](https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/tf/clip_by_norm)\r\n\r\n> t * clip_norm / l2norm(t)\r\n\r\nThe gradient seems `t / t * clip_norm`, right ? I think the result is undefined when t == 0.\r\n\r\n@alextp Could you please comment or reassign?"}